| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2046 — Recovery Inhibition (kairos)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0ffd3aa8-0bf8-50d5-9992-10c2ee31be07"
